responses.strategy: I tried to pay attention and notice which letters on the robots tended to be closer to 50/50 in terms of correct/incorrect and I opted not to press space bar for those.  Then I would devote more attention to the letters that more frequently needed a press of the spacebar...  For those letters, I would try to come up with a simple pneumonic.  For instance, it seemed that V and K required pressing the space bar, so I remembers V and K as 'Viking' but this was of limited.  However, for this game it was quite hard to predict each card/shape and it seemed like it was more frequent then 50% of the time.
